short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An easy-to-use password manager for creating, keeping and using secure passwords.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
My Financial Expert provides you with solutions that protect your digital privacy.  With Password Manager, you can manage and access account logins from a secure vault. An easy-to-use and convenient password manager that will enable you to create, store and use secure passwords in a way that integrates seamlessly.

Password Manager will keep your account logins secure and account access protected. Using it will help you:

Prevent hackers from accessing your account logins and financial information stored in the vault
Prevent hackers from guessing easy passwords and breaching your account.
Prevent phishing attacks by using the auto-login feature from the password manager
Types of data you can protect
Add your account logins, credit cards, and bank accounts to the password manager vault. Each will be encrypted and only accessible by you. Not even we can see your data stored in the vault. 

Available in My Financial Expert Elite bundle.
